AddressInfo.Title: West Street Car Park
AddressInfo.AccessComments:
Charger located to the left hand side of the entrance to the car park. Height restriction 2.0m preventing access for mobile vehicles or mobile homes
Customers must display a valid pay and display ticket whilst parked and charging.
Maximum stay up to 3hrs. 1hr - 60p/ 2hr -  £2.30/ 3hrs - £3.40
